Recommends: rtl-sdr
Description: Voice-activated amateur radio spotting tool
 Talk Spotter listens to radio audio streams, transcribes speech on-device
 using Vosk, and can post spots to the DX Cluster network via voice commands.
 .
 Supports RTL-SDR dongles and KiwiSDR web receivers.
